<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" data-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erreur - Mode Debug | IronFlow</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2a2a2a 100%);
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .error-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a2a2a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 
                0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
                0 0 20px rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .error-card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .error-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            color: #ff4d00;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff4d00;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .error-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .debug-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .debug-section {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .debug-section-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ff4d00;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .debug-content {
            font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #fff;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-all;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .error-button-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ff4d00 0%, #ff6b00 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .error-button-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .error-button-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .error-button-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-card">
            <div class="error-card-header">
                <div>
                    <svg class="error-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z" fill="currentColor"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h1 class="error-title">Erreur</h1>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="error-subtitle">Mode Debug</h2>
            <p class="error-message">Une erreur s'est produite. Voici les détails pour le débogage.</p>

            <div class="debug-info">
                <div class="debug-section">
                    <h3 class="debug-section-title">Message d'Erreur</h3>
                    <pre class="debug-content">{{ message }}</pre>
                </div>

                <div class="debug-section">
                    <h3 class="debug-section-title">Fichier</h3>
                    <pre class="debug-content">{{ file }}:{{ line }}</pre>
                </div>

                <div class="debug-section">
                    <h3 class="debug-section-title">Trace d'Appel</h3>
                    <pre class="debug-content">{{ trace }}</pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="error-actions">
                <a href="/" class="error-button error-button-primary">Retour à l'Accueil</a>
                <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="error-button error-button-secondary">Recharger la Page</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 